dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; prepared for the American Legion Weekly Bulletin by courtesy of the Automobile Club of Southern California.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways.
Belongs to a series of maps showing roads in California.
